title: Brow Power Universal Brow Pencil
description: Define and thicken brows with It Cosmetics Brow Powder for any brow color. Eyebrow pencil has an exclusive oval tip that creates a natural look while a patent-pending formulation boosts growth to thicken brows. Bonus brow brush. Waterproof. Hypoallergenic. Ingredients: Hydrogenated Coco Glycerides, Serenoa Serrulata Fruit Extract (Saw Palmetto), Biotin (Vitamin H), Urtica Dioica Leaf Powder (Nettle), Iron Oxides (77492), Ceresin, Equisetum Arvense (Horsetail) Extract, Lecithin, Pantothenic Acid, Camellia Sinensis Leaf Extract, Vitis Vinifera (Grape) Seed Extract, Euphorbia Cerifera (Candelilla) Wax, Copernicia Cerifera (Carnauba) Wax, Ascorbic Acid (Vitamin C), Tocopheryl Acetate, Beeswax (Apis Mellifera), Microcrystalline Wax, BHT, Retinyl Acetate. Usage: Apply lighter, softer strokes to match lighter color hair including blonde and silver. Press harder for darker color hair.
